          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-911-79L1-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-911-79L1-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-911-79L1-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">Written in or about the Year 1724.&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-911-79L1-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-911-79L1-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-911-79L1-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">XXVI. TO LADY CARTERET.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-911-79L1-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-911-79L1-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-911-79L1-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1">BY DR. SWIFT.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">F</hi>ROM India's burning clime I·'m brought,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-2" n="2">With cooling gales like Zephyrs fraught.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-3" n="3">Not Iris, when she paints the sky,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-4" n="4">Can shew more different hue than I;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-5" n="5">Nor can she change her form so fast,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-6" n="6">I·'m now a sail, and now a mast.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-7" n="7">I here am red, and there am green,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-8" n="8">A beggar there, and here a queen.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-9" n="9">I sometimes live in house of hair,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-10" n="10">And oft' in hand of lady fair.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-11" n="11">I please the young, I grace the old,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-12" n="12">And am at once both hot and cold.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-13" n="13">Say what I am then, if you can,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-79L1-line-14" n="14">And find the rhyme, and you·'re the man.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
